Description:
    Affinitve version of BBB (Backbone Boilerplate Build) with Backbone.LayoutManager. Out of the box it includes the following: jQuery, LoDash, Backbone, Backbone.LayoutManager, HandlebarsJS, Twitter Bootstrap for Compass, Modernizr, and HTML5 Boilerplate.


Example:
    yeoman init affin_bbb

    This will create:
      basic app scaffolding


    yeoman init affin_bbb:module NAME_OF_MODULE

    This will create:
        modules/NAME_OF_MODULE.js
